---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="How to Appear in Claude AI – UK Guide | Rank4AI" description="How to get your business recommended by Claude AI. Claude visibility guide for UK businesses.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Claude Optimisation' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">How to Appear in Claude AI</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Claude, built by Anthropic, draws from indexed web content and training data. It values clear entity definition and multiple independent sources describing the business consistently.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Claude tends to be more cautious than ChatGPT in its recommendations. It will often qualify its answers with caveats about verification. This means businesses with the strongest, most verifiable entity signals perform best.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What Claude Looks For</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Consistent entity definition</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Claude cross-references how a business is described across multiple sources. Inconsistency reduces confidence significantly.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Verifiable information</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Claude prioritises information it can verify from multiple independent sources. Claims that only appear on your own website carry less weight.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Structured expertise</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Depth of content in a specific area signals specialisation. Claude recommends specialists more confidently than generalists.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/learn/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Resources</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Guides</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
